":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1598935641","description":"<ol>\n<li>别人的 MergeRequest，都是干干净净，改了文件就是多少个 Change 。他的倒好，每次一上来就几十个 commit，几百个 change，认真一看，也就最上面那几个是他的。</li>\n<li>经常在工位上大喊「我的代码呢」，结果到头来查历史记录往往是被自己根本就没提交，或者被自己干掉了。</li>\n<li>同时也经常干掉别人的代码，自己完全不自知。出了问题，十有八九都是他干的。</li>\n<li>遇到问题就知道喊，有一次自己代码拉不下来了，说别人把 remote 搞坏了，所以自己拉不了了。喊人过去一看，工具上明明白白写着：you are in a middle of rebase，做个 abord 就好了。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>以上只是冰山一角，他写的代码我就懒得说了。我也不是针对谁，就事论事，和这种人共事，就是难受。祝大家都能找到更好的工作，避免遇到这种同事。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/711847","replies":110,"created_ts":1601438123,"created":"11:55:23","title":"十几年工作经验的老码农，连 git 都不会用。","author":"wxsm","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/wxsm","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6e74/4515/218737_mini.png?m=1514532703"},{"id":711755,"node":"广州","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/guangzhou","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/98f1/3708/20_mini.png?m=1542423096","description":"<p>路过广州计划去耍两天，时间不长，所以想问问大家看看有哪些好吃的一定要去的</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/711755","replies":108,"created_ts":1601428308,"created":"09:11:48","title":"十一计划去广州玩 2 天，求推荐必吃餐厅","author":"Rooney","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Rooney","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5abc/9858/75621_mini.png?m=1412061443"},{"id":711882,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1594743680","description":"<p>哈哈哈，广东省考公务员上岸，撒花，回复感谢送币</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/711882","replies":99,"created_ts":1601447649,"created":"14:34:09","title":"努力一年半，转行进度已完成 90%","author":"Marstin","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Marstin","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3ca6/13e0/360321_mini.png?m=1541383350"},{"id":711754,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1590337894","description":"<p>如题，进入 Reeder 官网，会提示 Reeder 5 马上发布，但是提供的 v4 的链接会提示在所在的区域不提供此 app，在已购列表里也消失了，不知道各位在外区 App Store 的情况如何？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/711754","replies":84,"created_ts":1601427833,"created":"09:03:53","title":"Reeder 4 在国区已经下架","author":"happyxyk","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/happyxyk","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a7f90187a8333fde8a182ae76012f7c4?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":711895,"node":"Java","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/java","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/03af/dbd6/63_mini.png?m=1596211530","description":"<p>//JDK 10 中新增了 var 局部变量推断的功能：</p>\n<p>//场景一：定义字符串\n//旧写法：</p>\n<p>String str = \"Hello, Java.\";</p>\n<p>//新写法：</p>\n<p>var s = \"Hello, Java.\";</p>\n<p>//PS：这里的旧写法指的是 JDK 10 之前的版本，而新写法指的是 JDK 10 以后（包含 JDK 10 ）的版本。</p>\n<p>//场景二：数值相加\n//旧写法：</p>\n<p>int num1 = 111;\ndouble num2 = 555.666d;\ndouble num3 = num1 + num2;\nSystem.out.println(num3);</p>\n<p>//PS：当遇到不同类型相加时（ int+ double ）会发生数据类型向上转型，因此 num3 就会升级为 double 类型。</p>\n<p>//新写法：</p>\n<p>var n1 = 111L;\nvar n2 = 555.666;\nvar n3 = n1 + n2;\nSystem.out.println(n3);</p>\n<p>//场景三：集合\n//旧写法：</p>\n<p>List&lt;Object&gt; list = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();\nlist.add(\"Hello\");\nlist.add(\"Java\");</p>\n<p>//新写法：</p>\n<p>var list = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();\nlist.add(\"Hello\");\nlist.add(\"Java\");\n//......</p>\n<p>//JavaScript：我慢慢靠近你，你慢慢靠近我，你中有我，我中有你，我特么谢谢你~</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/711895","replies":78,"created_ts":1601449228,"created":"15:00:28","title":"真是天道好轮回， Java 新特性：用 var 关键字，数据类型可以扔掉了？","author":"shew5689","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/shew5689","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/51760aaf632fefc074d18c7081288e45?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":711757,"node":"微信","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/wechat","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/55b3/7c5c/649_mini.png?m=1599634467","description":"<p>就是类似文章底部或朋友圈广告那种</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/711757","replies":68,"created_ts":1601428495,"created":"09:14:55","title":"丧心病狂！微信已经开始往订阅号信息流里面加广告了","author":"pianjiao","auth